WEBVTT

00:06.520 --> 00:11.120
There is no comparison, no equal

00:16.079 --> 00:19.440
Master, it's late

00:19.520 --> 00:23.440
We must hurry on our way…

00:24.840 --> 00:28.720
PLAY

00:28.800 --> 00:32.479
I wanted to be a loyal subject

00:32.560 --> 00:35.440
But after reaching this height

00:35.960 --> 00:39.320
What's left for those scholars?

00:39.400 --> 00:46.160
Why would they still crave official ranks?

00:49.840 --> 00:53.360
I think I've reached

00:54.080 --> 00:55.440
the end of my loyalty.

00:57.760 --> 00:59.080
What do you think,

00:59.160 --> 01:00.240
Your Highness?

01:01.280 --> 01:03.800
CROWN PRINCE, ZHU YOU SHENG

01:04.599 --> 01:07.720
Back then, my uncle, the Duke of Ding,

01:07.800 --> 01:11.360
and 237 members of the Jiang family
were framed and slaughtered.

01:12.560 --> 01:15.320
53,000 soldiers of the Duke of Ding's Army

01:15.400 --> 01:17.120
were disgraced and wronged.

01:18.280 --> 01:19.360
And today,

01:19.880 --> 01:21.640
I wonder how many in the Eastern Palace

01:21.720 --> 01:23.400
and the capital will be slaughtered?

01:24.880 --> 01:26.400
You defy the throne

01:27.680 --> 01:30.480
and aided Prince Qing
in his treacherous bid for power.

01:30.560 --> 01:32.080
It turns out this was all about

01:32.880 --> 01:34.920
clearing the name of
the Duke of Ding's Army.

01:36.320 --> 01:38.000
And you are blaming it

01:38.600 --> 01:41.600
on me and my father.

01:43.040 --> 01:45.280
When a ruler suspects his ministers,
they are doomed to die.

01:45.800 --> 01:47.960
Are you really saying I've wronged you?

01:48.040 --> 01:49.280
SONG MO

01:56.800 --> 01:57.920
Song Mo,

01:59.040 --> 02:00.760
I pity you.

02:00.840 --> 02:02.920
Your revenge is misplaced.

02:04.680 --> 02:06.000
I've lost,

02:07.480 --> 02:10.160
but in the end,
you'll lose everything as well.

02:20.280 --> 02:21.880
Your Highness!

02:25.520 --> 02:27.680
I would rather die

02:28.320 --> 02:30.080
than let a traitor have his way.

02:57.640 --> 02:59.360
General, we found it.

03:00.720 --> 03:01.560
Congratulations, sir.

03:01.640 --> 03:04.200
Grand General's blood feud
is half avenged.

03:12.200 --> 03:13.080
He said

03:14.160 --> 03:15.880
I took my revenge on the wrong people.

03:19.480 --> 03:21.240
In the winter of
the 27th year of Chengping's reign,

03:21.960 --> 03:24.040
as the Emperor was gravely ill,

03:24.120 --> 03:26.840
General of Agile Cavalry Song Mo
supported Prince Qing.

03:26.920 --> 03:28.480
Under the guise of tending to the Emperor,

03:28.560 --> 03:29.520
he launched an attack
on the capital at night.

03:29.600 --> 03:32.240
He sought to clear
the name of the Duke of Ding.

03:41.280 --> 03:42.800
Possessing over a hundred weapons
in secret is a grave crime.

03:42.880 --> 03:45.880
My Lady, did you know that Prince Qing
and General Song Mo would rebel?

03:45.960 --> 03:47.960
The capital is in chaos.

03:48.040 --> 03:49.560
The streets are filled with
rogue soldiers and refugees.

03:49.640 --> 03:52.480
When survival is at stake,
what use is talk of the law?

03:52.560 --> 03:54.120
-Grab them!
-Yes, ma'am!

04:02.680 --> 04:05.560
Song Mo is a ruthless killer.

04:05.640 --> 04:09.200
He even killed his own father and brother.

04:09.280 --> 04:12.120
Now he's leading rebel troops
back into the capital.

04:12.200 --> 04:15.400
Everyone's saying
he is going to massacre the entire city.

04:15.480 --> 04:17.320
I had to run for my life!

04:18.440 --> 04:19.839
How insolent!

04:19.920 --> 04:21.200
Matters of the court

04:21.279 --> 04:23.400
are not for a lowly servant
like you to gossip about.

04:23.480 --> 04:24.760
Flog him harder!

04:26.000 --> 04:27.600
Song Mo, that traitor…

04:28.600 --> 04:30.360
He's here for revenge.

04:39.960 --> 04:42.240
CHEN JIA

04:59.800 --> 05:00.960
WANG GE, EUNUCH OF
DIRECTORATE OF CEREMONIAL

05:12.240 --> 05:13.680
After tonight,

05:13.760 --> 05:15.760
Prince Qing will take the throne.

05:16.480 --> 05:18.880
General Song, you'll be credited
with the greatest merit.

05:19.400 --> 05:20.480
Allow me to offer

05:21.000 --> 05:22.760
my congratulations in advance.

05:22.840 --> 05:24.000
You should know

05:24.600 --> 05:25.800
that everything I've done

05:25.880 --> 05:28.120
is solely to clear
the Duke of Ding's name.

05:29.040 --> 05:30.760
Once I meet His Majesty,

05:30.840 --> 05:33.040
I'll hand this over to Prince Qing myself.

05:35.760 --> 05:38.520
His Majesty and His Highness
are having a private conversation.

05:38.600 --> 05:39.560
It wouldn't be proper to interrupt.

05:40.160 --> 05:41.440
Once His Highness ascends,

05:42.160 --> 05:44.360
an audience will be arranged for you.

05:45.120 --> 05:46.240
Very well.

05:48.920 --> 05:51.040
When he becomes the new ruler,

05:51.120 --> 05:52.160
tell him to come find me.

05:53.440 --> 05:55.160
All troops, hear my command!

05:55.240 --> 05:56.240
Yes, General!

05:56.800 --> 05:58.560
We will move to the outskirts of the city

05:59.760 --> 06:01.720
and await the Emperor's decree!

06:01.800 --> 06:02.840
Yes, General!

06:12.400 --> 06:14.280
With a new Emperor unable
to ascend the throne

06:14.360 --> 06:16.200
and a rebel army camped
outside the capital,

06:17.080 --> 06:19.480
it was a stalemate
that was chaos in disguise.

06:21.320 --> 06:22.960
At the time, I could never have imagined

06:23.040 --> 06:23.920
MARQUIS OF JINING'S RESIDENCE

06:24.000 --> 06:26.640
that the seemingly stable walls
of this household

06:27.240 --> 06:29.760
were already riddled with cracks.

06:30.880 --> 06:32.040
Starting tonight,

06:32.560 --> 06:34.800
halt all banquets,
entertainment, and repairs.

06:35.400 --> 06:37.240
Tomorrow, stewards will purchase

06:37.320 --> 06:40.240
a month's supply of provisions
for the household.

06:41.440 --> 06:43.760
Patrols will follow this route
around the estate

06:43.840 --> 06:44.680
in four rotating shifts.

06:44.760 --> 06:47.520
Ten armed guards are to stand watch
at the front and back gates,

06:48.120 --> 06:49.040
day and night.

06:49.680 --> 06:52.000
Post two guards outside
His Lordship's, Ming's,

06:52.080 --> 06:53.680
and the three concubines' quarters.

06:54.280 --> 06:55.120
Yes, My Lady.

06:55.200 --> 06:56.200
My Lady.

06:57.200 --> 06:59.320
His Lordship has ties to Prince Qing.

06:59.400 --> 07:00.960
Now, nobles, marquises,

07:01.040 --> 07:04.000
and ministers in the capital
are asking to see His Lordship.

07:04.800 --> 07:06.040
At a time like this,

07:06.120 --> 07:08.200
Prince Qing's faction wants
to crown a new emperor,

07:08.280 --> 07:10.480
while the loyal ministers are ready
to die defending the old one,

07:10.560 --> 07:12.240
And then there are the fence sitters,

07:12.760 --> 07:15.480
all eager to drag
His Lordship into the fray.

07:18.080 --> 07:19.160
Turn them away.

07:21.280 --> 07:22.600
But if I refuse to see them,

07:23.320 --> 07:24.920
I'm bound to offend them.

07:25.880 --> 07:27.080
Bring it in.

07:35.800 --> 07:37.000
I'm sick.

07:37.080 --> 07:38.200
Gravely ill.

07:38.800 --> 07:40.360
My Lord, you're too busy
tending to your ailing wife

07:41.120 --> 07:42.120
to receive guests.

07:42.200 --> 07:44.000
That's far too improper.

07:44.080 --> 07:45.920
What use is propriety
when the world is falling apart?

07:46.840 --> 07:49.800
Nothing matters more than life and death.

07:50.320 --> 07:51.200
With a coffin in place,

07:52.440 --> 07:53.640
they will leave you alone.

08:02.000 --> 08:05.280
FUNERAL TRIBUTE

09:45.680 --> 09:48.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL BLOSSOM
BY AUTHOR ZIZI FROM QIDIAN CHINESE WEBSITE

09:54.840 --> 09:56.720
Purchase 200 pounds
of silver frost charcoal.

09:56.800 --> 09:58.920
Since His Lordship and Ming
like calligraphy and painting,

09:59.000 --> 10:00.320
stock an additional
100 feet of jade paper.

10:00.400 --> 10:03.560
Also, have the stewards
from the estates and shops

10:03.640 --> 10:05.320
report back after lunch.

10:05.400 --> 10:06.760
Yes, My Lady.

10:07.600 --> 10:08.600
My Lady.

10:10.040 --> 10:11.080
Here.

10:13.720 --> 10:15.400
My Lady, you almost died

10:15.920 --> 10:17.640
when you had a miscarriage last year.

10:17.720 --> 10:19.440
Your priority now should be

10:19.520 --> 10:21.160
taking care of your health.

10:21.240 --> 10:22.760
You cannot overwork yourself.

10:27.160 --> 10:29.400
How can the matron of a noble family
neglect responsibilities?

10:30.520 --> 10:31.840
Serving my husband,

10:32.760 --> 10:34.520
looking after the concubines
and their children,

10:35.360 --> 10:37.200
managing over a hundred servants
in this household,

10:38.360 --> 10:40.720
along with dozens of
estates and businesses,

10:40.800 --> 10:42.000
there's no end to it.

10:42.760 --> 10:45.040
And that's not even counting
the endless social obligations.

10:45.920 --> 10:47.360
You're so unwell,

10:47.880 --> 10:50.040
yet His Lordship hasn't shown
the slightest concern.

10:50.120 --> 10:52.040
Fifth Young Lady came all this way

10:52.120 --> 10:53.720
claiming she'd help care for you,

10:53.800 --> 10:55.280
but she's nowhere to be seen.

10:55.800 --> 10:56.920
She's from another mother, after all.

10:57.000 --> 10:58.800
-No heart…
-Tuo Niang.

11:14.800 --> 11:16.000
My Lady, look.

11:16.080 --> 11:17.560
Spring hasn't even arrived,

11:17.640 --> 11:19.160
and the white magnolias
are already blooming.

11:19.240 --> 11:23.080
This is the first time I've seen
magnolias blooming in the snow.

11:24.520 --> 11:25.800
If my mother were here,

11:26.680 --> 11:28.080
she'd surely be delighted.

11:31.200 --> 11:33.160
If Seventh Madam were still with us,

11:33.880 --> 11:36.400
you wouldn't have
to bear all this burden alone.

11:45.560 --> 11:46.600
What is that smell?

11:48.680 --> 11:49.680
Medicinal herbs.

11:51.840 --> 11:53.360
The fragrance is strong.

11:56.000 --> 11:58.200
Looks like Ming hasn't been slacking off.

11:58.280 --> 11:59.760
She must be brewing medicine for me.

11:59.840 --> 12:00.800
You're right, My Lady.

12:00.880 --> 12:03.360
Don't bring up the matter
of different mothers again.

12:03.920 --> 12:06.040
It will upset Ming if she hears it.

12:06.120 --> 12:07.160
Yes, My Lady.

12:11.680 --> 12:13.360
The medicine might have burned.

12:23.000 --> 12:24.040
Don't worry.

12:24.120 --> 12:26.920
The doctor said she doesn't
have much time left.

12:27.000 --> 12:29.280
Once she's gone and
the mourning period is over,

12:30.680 --> 12:31.960
I'll marry you.

12:40.240 --> 12:41.520
He's not wrong.

12:43.760 --> 12:45.600
Our marriage was arranged by our parents,

12:46.320 --> 12:47.560
with no affection between us.

12:48.600 --> 12:50.200
If they really love each other,

12:51.720 --> 12:52.960
after I pass,

12:54.400 --> 12:55.800
his marriage to Dou Ming

12:57.000 --> 12:58.960
will benefit both our families.

12:59.760 --> 13:01.960
-It'll be a lasting alliance.
-Oh, My Lady…

13:03.240 --> 13:04.240
Let's go.

13:05.920 --> 13:07.240
But what if Father refuses?

13:08.200 --> 13:10.840
After all, her mother
and mine were sworn sisters.

13:11.480 --> 13:14.920
And her mother died because of
my mother's affair with my father.

13:17.640 --> 13:18.640
Mother…

13:19.520 --> 13:21.040
I can't believe
she's the reason Mother died.

13:27.120 --> 13:29.440
All my efforts to run this household,

13:30.320 --> 13:34.240
and in the end,
I've paved the way for my enemies.

13:35.720 --> 13:37.160
The kitchen is on fire.

13:37.680 --> 13:39.640
-Call the servants.
-Yes, My Lady.

13:41.240 --> 13:42.200
You can trust me.

13:42.800 --> 13:44.280
Don't you know me by now?

13:45.200 --> 13:47.120
Even if I have to go through hell,

13:47.200 --> 13:48.240
I'll marry you.

13:49.080 --> 13:50.160
No one can tear us apart.

13:58.920 --> 13:59.760
What's that noise?

14:00.560 --> 14:01.920
The kitchen is on fire!

14:02.720 --> 14:04.880
-Bring water!
-The kitchen is on fire!

14:05.400 --> 14:07.480
-Fire in the kitchen!
-Hurry up!

14:16.200 --> 14:19.520
My dear, it's my fault.
Please don't hurt Ming.

14:20.520 --> 14:21.720
I won't hurt her.

14:23.640 --> 14:25.240
In fact, I should thank you both.

14:26.280 --> 14:27.920
You've saved me from living in ignorance.

14:29.280 --> 14:31.640
-Sister…
-Don't call me that.

14:31.720 --> 14:34.120
I never expected love from my husband

14:35.160 --> 14:36.480
or the bond of sisterhood,

14:37.320 --> 14:38.200
but neither of you

14:38.720 --> 14:41.400
could even spare me
the smallest shred of decency.

14:41.480 --> 14:43.640
Tell me, how did my mother really die?

14:47.120 --> 14:48.920
That was before I was born.

14:49.000 --> 14:51.240
I've only overheard the elders mention it.

14:51.320 --> 14:52.880
I don't know the details.

14:54.240 --> 14:56.280
I will get to the bottom of it.

14:58.200 --> 15:00.040
But as for what's happened today,

15:00.840 --> 15:02.160
we will settle it here and now.

15:05.680 --> 15:06.520
You…

15:12.160 --> 15:14.920
I have been married
into this family for ten years.

15:15.000 --> 15:16.360
I've poured my heart

15:16.440 --> 15:18.280
into managing the household,

15:19.320 --> 15:22.280
never once failing
Wei Ting Yu or Dou Ming.

15:23.480 --> 15:24.960
Even amidst the chaos in the capital,

15:25.480 --> 15:27.520
I pushed through my illness
to protect this family.

15:27.600 --> 15:28.840
And yet,

15:29.360 --> 15:31.160
their adultery in broad daylight
in the kitchen

15:31.240 --> 15:32.680
has cursed me to an early death.

15:34.000 --> 15:36.400
A heartless man is unworthy of trust,

15:37.160 --> 15:39.040
and the daughter of
my enemy cannot be family.

15:39.800 --> 15:42.320
When this disgrace and betrayal
are brought to the court,

15:42.400 --> 15:43.440
you will all be my witnesses.

15:48.760 --> 15:49.640
From this moment on,

15:50.360 --> 15:52.160
I am no longer Marchioness of Jining.

16:01.720 --> 16:03.120
My Lord!

16:04.320 --> 16:06.160
My Lord, Her Ladyship
has left the residence.

16:06.240 --> 16:08.640
You think I don't know that?

16:08.720 --> 16:10.240
Didn't I ask you to guard the door?

16:10.320 --> 16:12.280
Why are you still standing there?
Go fetch our clothes!

16:12.360 --> 16:14.600
Yes, My Lord. Please excuse me.

16:18.240 --> 16:21.200
If I'd known it would come to this,
I should've listened to my mother!

16:21.280 --> 16:23.640
I should've put stronger poison
into her medicine

16:23.720 --> 16:24.720
and ended her for good!

16:27.640 --> 16:28.680
Why are you standing there?

16:29.280 --> 16:30.680
If she takes this to the authorities,

16:30.760 --> 16:32.040
Neither of us will have peace again.

16:32.120 --> 16:33.400
Don't worry.

16:33.920 --> 16:35.800
My family's century-old reputation

16:35.880 --> 16:37.800
won't be ruined by her.

16:43.960 --> 16:48.800
Such towering ambition is wasted in vain

16:49.320 --> 16:53.960
A lifetime's passion is never unchained

17:03.880 --> 17:06.119
Young Lady, it's snowing heavily.

17:16.160 --> 17:17.680
This isn't snow.

17:35.320 --> 17:37.360
Tuo Niang, give them some food.

17:40.840 --> 17:44.000
The land is in ruins,
the nation on the brink.

17:44.520 --> 17:45.680
Life is unpredictable.

17:46.760 --> 17:48.520
My departure this time

17:49.040 --> 17:50.080
marks our final farewell.

17:59.800 --> 18:01.280
The willows are alive,

18:01.360 --> 18:02.720
spinning the top.

18:02.800 --> 18:04.360
The willows are green,

18:04.440 --> 18:05.680
ringing the bell.

18:06.480 --> 18:08.840
The willows sprout, play…

18:15.000 --> 18:16.120
Tuo Niang.

18:17.360 --> 18:20.080
I was still young when my mother passed.

18:20.880 --> 18:23.560
Can you think of anything unusual
about that time?

18:24.760 --> 18:27.840
Your father had just passed
the imperial exams.

18:28.680 --> 18:30.560
And it was also
the birthday of your cousin.

18:31.200 --> 18:33.600
Your mother ordered me to take you

18:33.680 --> 18:35.680
to share the good news
with your uncle, Zhao Si.

18:36.200 --> 18:38.920
When we returned,
your mother had already passed away.

18:39.000 --> 18:41.320
Soon after, Wang Ying Xue
married your father.

18:43.160 --> 18:44.840
Tuo Niang, watch out!

19:21.760 --> 19:23.840
He has a spear that shatters the earth.

19:23.920 --> 19:25.400
He is a young man with white hair…

19:25.920 --> 19:27.080
Song Mo?

19:27.680 --> 19:29.600
Young Lady, are you hurt?

19:29.680 --> 19:30.760
Young Lady…

19:42.960 --> 19:44.040
Did you hear that?

19:44.720 --> 19:46.000
If you don't stop crying,

19:46.080 --> 19:48.080
I'll send you to
the big bad demon, Song Mo.

19:49.240 --> 19:50.680
He eats children.

19:52.640 --> 19:54.080
I'm not crying!

20:03.560 --> 20:04.560
Give me the food.

20:07.480 --> 20:08.600
Go home.

20:15.240 --> 20:19.080
He doesn't seem
as cruel as the rumors say.

20:19.600 --> 20:21.440
General, since you know your infamous name

20:21.520 --> 20:23.600
can stop children from crying,

20:24.280 --> 20:27.680
you should try to commit fewer sins.

20:32.720 --> 20:34.840
The carriage belongs to the
Marquis of Jining's Residence.

20:34.920 --> 20:36.800
LU MING

20:38.640 --> 20:40.320
With the capital in chaos,

20:41.160 --> 20:42.680
why have you come here?

20:45.360 --> 20:46.560
I'm going back to my hometown.

21:00.280 --> 21:01.320
Given your condition,

21:01.920 --> 21:03.120
the journey is too harsh for you.

21:03.800 --> 21:05.160
You might as well

21:05.240 --> 21:06.440
just return to to heaven.

21:08.600 --> 21:09.880
Come to the temple and rest,

21:10.840 --> 21:12.200
warm yourself with hot medicinal soup.

21:14.600 --> 21:15.720
Hold on.

21:15.800 --> 21:16.800
In such times,

21:16.880 --> 21:19.200
how can we shelter people we barely know?

21:19.280 --> 21:20.160
Lu Zheng.

21:39.880 --> 21:41.640
-Soldiers, hear my command!
-Yes, General!

21:41.720 --> 21:43.200
Move to the rear mountain of Wanfo Temple!

21:43.280 --> 21:44.320
Yes, General!

21:47.920 --> 21:50.320
I mistook you for an enemy scout earlier.

21:50.400 --> 21:51.240
I apologize for the offense.

21:52.560 --> 21:53.560
Lu Ming,

21:54.960 --> 21:58.120
repair the carriage and
escort Her Ladyship to the temple.

21:58.200 --> 21:59.240
Yes, General!

22:00.320 --> 22:01.320
Young Lady.

22:35.920 --> 22:38.440
The carriage only contains valuables.

22:50.480 --> 22:52.080
The snow makes the roads treacherous.

22:52.160 --> 22:53.000
What's so urgent

22:53.880 --> 22:55.360
that you had to travel
in your poor health?

22:57.680 --> 22:59.080
It's a private family matter,

22:59.160 --> 23:00.560
not something we can share.

23:01.160 --> 23:02.320
The General has shown kindness,

23:03.040 --> 23:04.080
offering shelter from the snow.

23:04.920 --> 23:06.560
Yet you still refuse to be open.

23:06.640 --> 23:08.520
-Are you hiding something?
-Lu Ming.

23:11.960 --> 23:13.000
Young Lady…

23:14.360 --> 23:15.200
My Lady, surely you know

23:15.960 --> 23:17.480
that the nation's fate
will soon be decided.

23:18.160 --> 23:20.360
At such times, when survival is at stake,

23:23.160 --> 23:24.600
everything must be analyzed.

23:26.280 --> 23:28.200
-General…
-Tuo Niang.

23:31.520 --> 23:33.240
It's nothing particularly important.

23:33.960 --> 23:35.920
I just feared that, should I speak of it,

23:36.000 --> 23:37.840
it would offend your ears.

23:38.840 --> 23:42.000
Marquis of Jining and my half-sister

23:42.640 --> 23:44.160
have been committing adultery

23:44.240 --> 23:45.200
while I've been ill.

23:46.080 --> 23:47.440
I caught them today.

23:48.280 --> 23:49.880
I intended to divorce him immediately,

23:50.640 --> 23:53.720
but there is no one in the Office of
State Affairs who can process my case

23:53.800 --> 23:55.120
due to the chaos in the capital.

23:56.040 --> 23:57.040
So,

23:57.800 --> 23:59.160
I must return home and report it.

24:01.640 --> 24:02.920
I see.

24:03.760 --> 24:06.720
Forgive my rudeness, My Lady.

24:07.400 --> 24:08.760
Your apology is not needed.

24:11.560 --> 24:13.160
I'm no longer Marchioness of Jining.

24:14.520 --> 24:15.840
My surname is Dou,

24:17.520 --> 24:18.560
and I'm the fourth child in my family.

24:21.000 --> 24:24.040
A man can leave a woman easily,

24:24.120 --> 24:26.360
while it's harder
for a woman to leave a man.

24:26.960 --> 24:28.400
The sooner you see someone's true colors,

24:28.480 --> 24:29.920
the sooner you can cut ties.

24:34.920 --> 24:36.240
Young Lady Dou,

24:36.760 --> 24:38.480
you are the luckiest among the unlucky.

24:41.600 --> 24:43.920
General, you control the new dynasty

24:44.000 --> 24:44.840
and hold unparalleled power,

24:46.480 --> 24:48.520
yet why has your hair turned gray,

24:49.080 --> 24:51.320
and your eyes filled with regret?

24:55.560 --> 24:56.960
General!

25:00.440 --> 25:01.600
General…

25:08.160 --> 25:09.120
Forgive me.

25:10.440 --> 25:12.120
I'm a dying man
who has squandered his efforts

25:12.840 --> 25:14.320
on those who did not deserve them.

25:18.840 --> 25:20.000
Indeed.

25:20.760 --> 25:22.160
We have squandered our efforts

25:23.920 --> 25:25.440
on those who do not deserve them.

25:36.600 --> 25:37.720
It will soon be dawn.

25:38.320 --> 25:40.840
I'll have my men escort you back
to your hometown, Young Lady Dou.

25:42.280 --> 25:43.560
Today's celestial signs are strange.

25:44.720 --> 25:46.040
The comet enters the Purple Star,

25:46.120 --> 25:47.640
an omen of disaster and turmoil,

25:47.720 --> 25:50.000
yet we also see shooting stars
streaking across the sky.

25:50.080 --> 25:51.040
The unrest in the capital

25:51.120 --> 25:52.960
certainly corresponds
with the comet's entry,

25:53.560 --> 25:54.760
but the shooting stars…

26:00.600 --> 26:02.320
They might signal
fortune lies within misfortune.

26:02.400 --> 26:04.200
You two are intertwined in fate.

26:06.280 --> 26:07.960
You overestimate me, Reverend Yuan Tong.

26:08.960 --> 26:11.480
I am just a powerless woman,

26:12.000 --> 26:14.240
merely a passerby
seeking a bowl of medicinal soup

26:14.320 --> 26:16.200
and shelter from the snowstorm.

26:16.800 --> 26:20.120
How could I possibly be entwined
with General Song's fate?

26:34.200 --> 26:35.360
What is this?

26:35.440 --> 26:38.160
Prince Qing won't even appear
to tell me the truth?

26:41.480 --> 26:42.760
General Song,

26:42.840 --> 26:44.600
no matter how great your achievements,

26:44.680 --> 26:45.880
after what you did,

26:46.480 --> 26:47.960
His Highness has no choice

26:48.040 --> 26:49.920
but to give you a death sentence.

26:50.960 --> 26:52.800
Those who take the throne

26:52.880 --> 26:54.400
are equally cold and ungrateful.

26:55.040 --> 26:57.840
The Duke of Ding fought
on the frontlines for 15 years,

26:57.920 --> 26:59.640
only to be framed for treason

26:59.720 --> 27:01.000
and have his entire family executed.

27:01.080 --> 27:03.800
Prince Qing hasn't even
taken the throne yet,

27:04.320 --> 27:06.760
and he's already setting out
to eliminate his allies.

27:07.440 --> 27:09.760
Doesn't he fear
what people will say about him?

27:13.200 --> 27:15.040
General Song, don't worry about that.

27:15.120 --> 27:16.320
If this gets out,

27:16.400 --> 27:19.840
it'll be nothing but a scandal
of the Marquis of Jining's family.

27:20.520 --> 27:23.520
What does it have to do with Prince Qing?

27:24.880 --> 27:26.560
Don't you agree, My Lord?

27:32.280 --> 27:34.640
By order of Prince Qing,

27:35.240 --> 27:39.000
Song Mo has grown
arrogant with his merits.

27:39.080 --> 27:42.520
He seduced Marchioness of Jining,
Dou Zhao, and ran off with her.

27:43.240 --> 27:44.680
Wei Ting Yu, you…

27:44.760 --> 27:47.760
With all the evidence, they shall
be executed to set things right.

27:50.360 --> 27:52.000
He's shifting the blame onto a woman.

27:52.600 --> 27:55.640
Prince Qing is even more
shameless than his father.

27:55.720 --> 27:56.840
General Song,

27:57.360 --> 28:00.000
if you surrender the imperial seal

28:00.080 --> 28:01.080
and end your life now,

28:01.680 --> 28:05.680
His Highness may
leave you with a whole corpse.

28:06.280 --> 28:07.680
Too bad.

28:07.760 --> 28:08.960
I'm far too petty

28:09.560 --> 28:11.520
to leave you with a whole corpse.

28:20.360 --> 28:25.320
Kill!

28:32.280 --> 28:34.840
My Lady, please come with me
to the back mountain.

28:35.440 --> 28:37.120
Come on, we have to go.

28:40.240 --> 28:41.680
When Prince Qing stopped me
from seeing His Majesty,

28:42.520 --> 28:44.440
I knew then he intended
to kill me after using me.

28:44.520 --> 28:46.040
-Eunuch…
-I gave him a chance.

28:46.680 --> 28:48.560
Had he kept his promise
and come to meet me,

28:49.080 --> 28:50.840
I would've let him live.

28:51.360 --> 28:53.280
But instead, he went to
the Western Mountain palace.

28:53.360 --> 28:55.080
WESTERN MOUNTAIN PALACE

28:55.160 --> 28:56.920
It proves that my efforts

28:57.000 --> 28:59.920
to deploy the Duke of Ding's
elite troops there weren't in vain.

29:00.680 --> 29:02.680
What benefit would killing me
bring to Song Mo?

29:03.280 --> 29:04.360
If he wants to usurp the regency,

29:04.960 --> 29:06.560
I will grant it to him.

29:06.640 --> 29:10.120
-Kill!
-Kill!

29:11.720 --> 29:12.720
Prince Qing

29:13.600 --> 29:15.680
is probably a corpse by now.

29:20.160 --> 29:23.280
Empty threats. Seize him!

29:28.760 --> 29:30.520
Eunuch Wang…

29:38.520 --> 29:40.480
-Prepare for battle!
-Prepare for battle!

29:40.560 --> 29:42.880
Kill!

29:48.040 --> 29:49.200
Young Lady…

29:51.000 --> 29:52.120
Careful.

30:22.240 --> 30:23.680
The Duke of Ding's Army has
always been skilled in battle.

30:23.760 --> 30:26.200
Now that we've been surrounded,
what are we going to do?

30:26.280 --> 30:28.880
Don't worry. As long as your wife is dead,

30:29.560 --> 30:31.000
no matter how capable Song Mo is,

30:31.080 --> 30:32.280
he'll just be a general
who has committed a crime.

30:34.680 --> 30:35.680
My Lord!

31:36.520 --> 31:38.280
Young Lady, run!

31:46.920 --> 31:48.320
I'm going to kill you!

31:51.920 --> 31:54.880
You're just a weak woman,

31:55.440 --> 31:57.000
who can you possibly kill?

32:17.600 --> 32:18.960
Tuo Niang!

33:11.080 --> 33:12.160
General!

33:16.400 --> 33:19.400
General, I really didn't know
Wei Ting Yu would do that.

33:23.120 --> 33:24.720
I'm poisoned.

33:25.360 --> 33:26.480
My time is running out.

33:27.360 --> 33:28.960
I only regret that I can't clear

33:29.040 --> 33:31.200
the Duke of Ding's name before I die.

33:31.720 --> 33:33.480
Instead, I've dragged you into this

33:33.560 --> 33:36.040
and led you to bear this disgrace,
costing you your life.

33:36.680 --> 33:38.080
You saved my life

33:39.200 --> 33:41.000
in the fields last night.

33:44.160 --> 33:45.440
It's I who brought you trouble.

33:47.240 --> 33:49.240
Come, let me take you away.

33:58.840 --> 33:59.840
Yuan Tong…

33:59.920 --> 34:00.760
Reverend Yuan Tong!

34:02.200 --> 34:03.240
Yuan Tong.

34:21.920 --> 34:24.120
RECORD OF TRUTHS

34:24.199 --> 34:25.400
Go.

34:26.239 --> 34:27.320
Go.

34:27.400 --> 34:28.880
-That way.
-Let's go together.

34:28.960 --> 34:30.000
I don't matter.

34:30.080 --> 34:33.040
Within misfortune lies fortune.
You two are bound by fate.

34:33.120 --> 34:34.440
The course of destiny
is now in your hands.

34:35.360 --> 34:37.600
Go now. Go!

34:37.679 --> 34:40.760
They're over there! Get them!

35:09.640 --> 35:10.720
Watch out!

35:48.920 --> 35:52.040
To live as a woman is to
live at the mercy of others.

35:52.840 --> 35:56.560
A lifetime of joys and sorrows
controlled by someone else.

35:59.400 --> 36:02.640
It is not only in marriage
that one is bound.

36:04.280 --> 36:07.280
Even rulers and ministers
are no different.

36:09.720 --> 36:11.280
One moment you're favored,

36:12.960 --> 36:14.920
the next, you're sentenced to death.

36:30.520 --> 36:32.040
Throughout my whole life,

36:32.840 --> 36:34.720
I never had a moment

36:34.800 --> 36:36.240
RECORD OF TRUTHS

36:36.320 --> 36:38.080
when I could choose my own fate.

37:37.200 --> 37:38.320
You're finally awake.

37:38.400 --> 37:39.720
You were so absorbed in your reading,

37:39.800 --> 37:41.560
you bumped straight into the mirror frame.

37:57.560 --> 37:58.600
I…

37:59.240 --> 38:00.240
How…

38:00.760 --> 38:01.880
Shou Gu?

38:03.360 --> 38:04.240
Young Lady?

38:05.400 --> 38:07.480
-Shou Gu.
-Young Lady.

38:07.560 --> 38:08.800
ZHAO GU QIU, MATRON OF DOU FAMILY

38:08.880 --> 38:10.200
You're awake.

38:22.840 --> 38:24.120
Mother?

38:28.280 --> 38:29.560
Tuo Niang?

38:36.560 --> 38:38.160
You're still here!

38:45.400 --> 38:48.160
Why are you acting like a little girl?

38:53.520 --> 38:55.080
It's all my fault.

38:55.800 --> 38:58.160
Madam went to pray to
the Buddha to bless Master

38:58.240 --> 39:00.120
with success in the imperial exams,

39:00.200 --> 39:02.240
and I went with her.

39:02.320 --> 39:04.000
I should've kept watch over Young Lady.

39:04.520 --> 39:06.600
Success in the exams?

39:07.520 --> 39:09.760
Is this the eighth year
of the reign Chengping?

39:12.280 --> 39:13.400
Yes.

39:15.480 --> 39:17.680
But I clearly lived through a lifetime.

39:18.800 --> 39:20.040
Just now,

39:20.840 --> 39:23.120
the temple was filled with Jiying Guards.

39:23.840 --> 39:25.800
I died right in front of the mirror.

39:27.640 --> 39:28.920
Young Lady…

39:29.720 --> 39:32.160
Sometimes, a dream seems
so real that it feels like reality.

39:32.240 --> 39:33.680
But it's still just a dream.

39:34.200 --> 39:37.120
You got too caught up in the stories

39:37.200 --> 39:39.040
and bumped your head.

39:39.120 --> 39:41.320
The story is just a story,
but you are real.

39:45.760 --> 39:48.000
Record of Truths?

39:48.640 --> 39:50.960
It's a book left by a carefree recluse,

39:51.040 --> 39:52.880
meant for someone destined to find it.

39:54.480 --> 39:56.760
Looks like you're that lucky one.

39:56.840 --> 39:58.920
Thank you, Master Yuan Tong.

40:01.000 --> 40:02.560
You're Yuan Tong?

40:13.040 --> 40:14.080
Mo!

40:17.760 --> 40:19.000
You're finally awake.

40:20.520 --> 40:21.360
Mo,

40:21.960 --> 40:24.320
I couldn't wake you from a nightmare.
I was worried sick.

40:24.400 --> 40:26.480
Fortunately, the abbot calmed
your spirit and treated you.

40:27.200 --> 40:29.400
How do you feel now?

40:29.480 --> 40:30.320
DUCHESS OF YING, JIANG HUI SUN

40:31.000 --> 40:32.400
Mother,

40:32.480 --> 40:35.240
I had such a long dream.

40:36.240 --> 40:38.520
But now I can't remember

40:38.600 --> 40:39.920
anything from it.

40:40.880 --> 40:42.120
It's just as well.

40:42.760 --> 40:44.520
All living beings

40:44.600 --> 40:46.440
have the wisdom and nature
of the Buddha within them.

40:47.040 --> 40:49.480
It is only because
of delusion and attachment

40:50.000 --> 40:51.040
that they cannot attain enlightenment.

40:51.960 --> 40:52.840
Thank you, Abbot.

40:54.360 --> 40:55.600
But I feel like there are things

40:57.400 --> 40:58.800
I shouldn't have forgotten.

41:04.720 --> 41:07.520
On the day of triumphant success,
the spring breeze brings joy,

41:07.600 --> 41:10.440
But the magnolia withers in autumn.

41:10.960 --> 41:13.880
The aspiring ones soar with the wind,

41:14.400 --> 41:17.480
yet regretful, they choose the coldest
branches in the best of times.

41:18.000 --> 41:19.920
Triumphant in the imperial exams,

41:20.000 --> 41:22.160
yet why does it speak
of withering and decline?

41:43.280 --> 41:44.120
Shou Gu.

41:46.760 --> 41:48.040
What are you reading?

41:49.760 --> 41:51.760
Is this book that interesting?

41:53.000 --> 41:54.040
He made it…

41:55.200 --> 41:57.080
-He made it?
-Madam!

41:58.400 --> 41:59.480
Madam!

42:00.000 --> 42:01.640
Master made it!

42:03.160 --> 42:04.760
Master made it onto the list!
The seventh in the second division!

42:07.400 --> 42:08.880
This is wonderful!

42:08.960 --> 42:10.480
Shi Ying's hard work

42:10.560 --> 42:12.280
has finally paid off.

42:14.320 --> 42:15.680
Shou Gu,

42:15.760 --> 42:16.960
how did you know your father succeeded?

42:18.200 --> 42:20.920
-I…
-This temple is so miraculous.

42:21.600 --> 42:22.600
You even came to pray for

42:22.680 --> 42:24.920
Young Lady Wang Ying Xue's family
matters before, Madam.

42:25.000 --> 42:26.360
-Wang Ying Xue?
-It's just like today.

42:29.680 --> 42:31.280
After studying diligently for years.

42:31.360 --> 42:33.760
Father finally succeeded
in the imperial exam that year.

42:34.360 --> 42:36.040
When we were celebrating,

42:36.560 --> 42:37.880
Mother fell ill.

42:37.960 --> 42:40.320
Mother? Are you all right, Mother?

42:40.400 --> 42:41.600
Soon after she died,

42:42.120 --> 42:45.400
Wang Ying Xue married into
the family and became my stepmother.

42:45.480 --> 42:48.520
After all, her mother
and mine were sworn sisters.

42:48.600 --> 42:52.840
And her mother died because of
my mother's affair with my father.

42:53.600 --> 42:55.680
Gao Sheng, prepare the horse.

42:55.760 --> 42:56.800
Yes, Madam.

42:57.680 --> 42:59.160
Tuo Niang, take Shou Gu

42:59.240 --> 43:01.240
to the Zhao residence to deliver
the good news to my brother.

43:01.320 --> 43:02.520
It happens to be Zhang Ru's birthday…

43:02.600 --> 43:03.480
No.

43:05.360 --> 43:07.040
It's been such a long time
since I saw Father.

43:07.640 --> 43:10.080
Why not invite Uncle
and Zhang Ru to our home

43:10.160 --> 43:11.240
to celebrate together?

43:11.320 --> 43:12.400
Uncle is an Imperial Censor

43:12.480 --> 43:14.160
with the power to impeach officials.

43:14.240 --> 43:15.840
He reports directly to His Majesty.

43:15.920 --> 43:17.960
Father's future career
will benefit from connections.

43:20.880 --> 43:23.600
When did you become so
knowledgeable about such things?

43:25.800 --> 43:29.520
Alright then. I haven't seen
my brother in a long time either.

43:29.600 --> 43:31.160
Please invite him then.

43:32.120 --> 43:33.200
When I married into this family,

43:33.280 --> 43:36.080
I buried a jar of
Huadiao wine for Shi Ying.

43:36.160 --> 43:37.920
It's finally time to open it.

43:38.000 --> 43:39.000
I must thank the gods.

43:39.600 --> 43:41.040
Give it to me.

43:42.360 --> 43:43.440
Walk slowly.

43:45.200 --> 43:47.400
Tuo Niang, the imperial exams
were held in the capital.

43:47.480 --> 43:49.520
Is Wang Ying Xue
also living in the capital?

43:49.600 --> 43:50.680
Yes.

43:50.760 --> 43:52.880
Young Lady Wang's father was demoted,

43:52.960 --> 43:54.200
and her family fell on hard times.

43:54.280 --> 43:56.800
She had to sell cotton and rice
to support her family in Chaxi.

43:57.400 --> 43:58.800
When Master was studying in Chaxi,

43:58.880 --> 44:01.840
Madam even asked him to bring
some money for Young Lady Wang.

44:04.640 --> 44:06.200
Quickly, invite Uncle over.

44:06.280 --> 44:07.240
The sooner, the better.

44:08.840 --> 44:09.840
Yes, Young Lady.

44:17.800 --> 44:19.560
The past cannot be changed,

44:20.080 --> 44:22.200
but the future can still be made.

44:22.960 --> 44:23.800
Since Record of Truths

44:24.720 --> 44:26.720
records this so-called fate,

44:27.480 --> 44:29.080
and now that I possess it

44:30.160 --> 44:31.840
and can foresee the ending,

44:31.920 --> 44:33.920
I can change it.

44:36.040 --> 44:37.320
Mother,

44:37.400 --> 44:39.120
however difficult or dangerous it may be,

44:39.200 --> 44:40.040
I will protect you.

44:41.360 --> 44:43.280
I won't let anyone hurt you.

45:00.960 --> 45:04.320
When Dou Shi Ying was studying,
he committed adultery!

45:04.400 --> 45:06.040
If you pressure my sister again,

45:06.120 --> 45:07.920
I'll risk my life

45:08.000 --> 45:10.600
to make sure we go down together!

45:10.680 --> 45:12.040
If you really won't forgive me,

45:12.120 --> 45:14.400
then grant me a white silk ribbon
so I can hang myself.

45:14.480 --> 45:16.880
If you really want to die… Here.

47:06.000 --> 47:07.000
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
DURING THE MAKING OF THIS FILM

47:07.080 --> 47:08.680
MEDICAL ACTS AND DRUGS IN THIS DRAMA
ARE FICTIONAL. DO NOT IMITATE.
